      "rationale": "Code verification performed using the Method of Manufactured Solutions (MMS) for the incompressible Navier-Stokes equations in a rotating reference frame. Observed order of accuracy (1.97 for velocity, 1.94 for pressure) is consistent with the nominal second-order spatial discretization scheme. No coding errors identified. Level 2 achieved."
