      "rationale": "Three mesh levels (3.2M, 7.8M, 18.4M hexahedral cells) were generated with a refinement ratio of approximately 1.33. GCI for NIH at the worst-case operating point (3 L/min / 3500 RPM) is 3.1%, satisfying the 5% criterion. y+ < 1 maintained on all rotating surfaces. Discretization error level 2 achieved."
