    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 guidance for medium model influence at MRL 2. NIH predictions agree with benchmark experimental data within 15% across all five CPB operating points, and RH < 1 for all nominal-geometry configurations. The FDA generic centrifugal pump benchmark dataset provides strong geometric correspondence with the simulation, and the supporting WSS validation against the Hariharan et al. dataset further corroborates shear-field fidelity. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model has sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device as specified in the COU. Decision: Accepted.",
